            <h2>Ereshkigal</h2>
            <p class="subtitle" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">Queen of the Great Below, Lady of Kur</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Ereshkigal is the absolute sovereign of Kur, the Land of No Return. She is the dark sister of Inanna, ruling the realm of the dead with impartial harshness. In her domain, all humans‚Äîking and slave, hero and coward‚Äîface the same dusty fate. Even gods who enter Kur fall under her power. She embodies the inevitability of death and the finality of mortality. Her name means "Great Lady of the Great Below."</p>
        </section>

